Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.properties

Class GovernanceActionTypeElement

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.properties.GovernanceActionTypeElement
public class GovernanceActionTypeElement extends Object
GovernanceActionTypeElement contains the properties and header for a governance action type entity retrieved from the metadata repository.
